<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    /* ======================================== */
    /* 1. GLOBAL STYLES */
    /* ======================================== */
    body { 
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6; 
      color: #1a1a1a;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }
    
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 40px auto; 
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px; /* Consistent rounded corners */
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); /* Soft floating shadow */
      border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 2. HEADER (The Alerting Color) */
    /* ======================================== */
    .header { 
      /* Using a deep, modern maroon/red color for finality */
      background-color: #991b1b; 
      color: #ffffff; 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 4px solid #f87171; /* Lighter red accent */
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 3. CONTENT */
    /* ======================================== */
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }
    .content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    
    /* List of Implications */
    .content ul {
      margin: 20px 0;
      padding-left: 20px;
      color: #1a1a1a;
      background: #f9fafb; /* Light background for the list */
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    .content li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #4b5563;
    }
    
    /* Contact/Reactivation Button */
    .btn-reactivate {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      background-color: #636b2f; /* Using the Brand Primary color for the positive action (Reactivate) */
      color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 6px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .btn-reactivate:hover {
      background-color: #4f5625;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 4. REASON BOX (Highlighting the core reason) */
    /* ======================================== */
    .reason-box { 
      background: #fff5f5; /* Light red/pink */
      border-left: 4px solid #d9534f; /* Strong Red Accent */
      padding: 16px 20px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .reason-box p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #2d3748;
    }
    .reason-box p strong {
      color: #d9534f;
    }

    /* ======================================== */
    /* 5. FOOTER */
    /* ======================================== */
    .footer { 
      text-align: center; 
      padding: 20px 30px; 
      background: #f9fafb;
      color: #6b7280; 
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }
    
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f5f5f5;">
  <div class="container" style="background-color: #ffffff;">
    
    <div class="header" style="background-color: #991b1b; color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-bottom: 4px solid #f87171;">
      <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700;">Account Deactivated</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content" style="padding: 40px 30px;">
      <p style="font-size: 16px;">Hello,</p>
      <p style="font-size: 16px;">This confirms that your FormaChat account was deactivated on <strong>{{deactivatedAt}}</strong>.</p>
      
      {{#if reason}}
      <div class="reason-box" style="background-color: #fff5f5; border-left: 4px solid #d9534f; padding: 16px 20px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 25px 0;">
        <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #2d3748;"><strong style="color: #d9534f;">Reason:</strong> {{reason}}</p>
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">What this means:</p>
      <ul style="margin: 20px 0; padding: 20px 20px 20px 40px; border-radius: 8px; background-color: #f9fafb; list-style-type: none;">
        <li style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563;">‚ùå You can no longer access your account.</li>
        <li style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563;">üö´ All your AI support agents have been disabled.</li>
        <li style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #4b5563;">‚úÖ You will not be charged for any future payments.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="font-size: 16px;">If you believe this was a mistake or would like to reactivate your account, please use the link below:</p>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
        <a href="mailto:support@formachat.com?subject=Reactivate%20My%20FormaChat%20Account" class="btn-reactivate" 
           style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 25px; background-color: #636b2f; color: #ffffff; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
           Reactivate Account
        </a>
      </div>

      <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 16px;">We're sorry to see you go,<br>The FormaChat Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer" style="background-color: #f9fafb; color: #6b7280; padding: 20px 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;">&copy; {{currentYear}} FormaChat. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p style="margin: 5px 0;">For support, please email support@formachat.com</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>